videos.description: Briante Weber gets the steal on Kyrie Irving and takes it for the easy score.
videos.headline: Weber picks Kyrie's pocket

videos.headline: Ariza knocks down 3 plus the foul

videos.description: Kyrie Irving breaks through a couple defenders and gets the layup to go.

videos.description: James Harden drives on Kyrie Irving and scores after the ball goes off the shot clock.The basket would not count.
videos.headline: Harden makes circus shot

videos.description: Kyrie Irving steps-through the defense as the Celtics make a run in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Irving Eurosteps into the lane for the score

videos.description: Terry Rozier gets the steal and throws down the emphatic dunk as the Celtics inch closer to the Rockets lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Rozier slams it home after big steal) 2017/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rozier slams it home after big steal

videos.description: James Harden hits a step-back 3-pointer late in the shot clock for the Rockets.
videos.headline: Harden nails a dagger

videos.description: A pair of offensive fouls from James Harden in the final 10 seconds set up Al Horford's go-ahead basket as the Celtics steal a win with a 26-point comeback, which is the largest comeback in the NBA this season.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Celtics steal win over Rockets) 2017/12/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Celtics pull off epic rally in Boston
